<HEADLINE> London Stock Prices Fall / British Stocks  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	LONDON (AP) -- Share prices fell on the London Stock Exchange on  
Friday. 
</P>
<P>
	The Financial Times-Stock Exchange 100-share index fell 31.4  
points, or 0.5 percent, to 6,175.1. 
</P>
<P>
	Provisional volume was 980.9 million shares compared with 1.094  
billion. 
</P>
