complaint to the U.N. Security Council over the seizure, praised 
the students' action, presidential palace officials said. 
</P>
<P>
	This is the first time since 1985 that the Israelis expanded the  
zone by setting a fence and ordering residents to go through a 
checkpoint. 
</P>
<P>
	Lebanese guerrillas have been fighting to end the occupation.  
</P>
